data.description: Step into the Epitome of refined living in this Exquisite 4-bedroom, 3-bath home situated in a Gated Community in Bradenton, Florida. Constructed in 2018 by Maronda Homes, this residence seamlessly blends modern Elegance with thoughtful Design.  Admire the Upgrades throughout the Entire Home from the Glass Door entrance to Stunning Tile Flooring throughout the home. The Gourmet Kitchen, complete with GE Stainless Steel Appliances, a Double Oven, and a captivating glass tile backsplash, effortlessly combines style and practicality. A Large Kitchen Island takes center stage, offering both a focal point and a functional space for culinary creativity.  The Open Floor plan of the home ensures a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining area, and living space. This design not only enhances the overall sense of spaciousness but also promotes a welcoming atmosphere, perfect for both entertaining guests and daily family life.  As you enter, notice the convenience of the Extended driveway that leads to this prime Pond Lot location, offering tranquil Water Views that enhance the overall ambiance. Beyond being a home, this residence embodies a lifestyle. The 3-car garage, featuring an epoxy-coated floor and a handy wash tub, adds a touch of practical luxury to your daily routine.  What truly distinguishes this property is its location in a gated community with an exceptionally LOW HOA fee. This fee covers internet, cable TV, and grants access to community amenities, including a pool and clubhouse, creating an ultra-fi community where connectivity meets leisure.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this MOVE-IN-ready home yours. With its superb location, providing easy access to everything, including stunning Beaches, this residence invites you to embrace the lifestyle you deserve in a thoughtfully crafted space.
